# AI Agent Rules

## Architecture
- Use Vercel AI SDK
- Use tool calling
- Use Zod schemas for all tools

## Agent Behavior
- Agents must retrieve data through tools
- Avoid passing all context in a single prompt
- Prefer multi-step reasoning through tool usage

## Requirements
- Use at least 3 tools
- Use maxSteps >= 3
- Use streaming responses

## OpnameBuddy

The DailyBuddy agent may use:

- getPatientCheckins
- getPatientRestrictions
- getAvailableActivities
- getActivityFeedback
- getOpenQuestions
- saveDailyAdvice

The AI must never provide medical diagnoses or treatment recommendations.

The AI may only support recovery participation within caregiver-defined boundaries.